name: 07. LUST
description:
7/7 from "7 Deadly Sins" collection.

The nose over your dark skin, a subtle wood flavor, because of how intense you play, get your body at the stake. 
My fingers they sound, and they get dizzy and they return to my own mouth, like a bee to its hive, with pollen on its legs feeding a new queen.
That honey you leave has an owner, may you know. The one that gets into your head and soaks those proposals, from the doubts of your essence
to the cold of what is new, where a storm rises. Please don't be afraid, it is normal, if it does happen, then it is worth it.

Full story: naranjabrasa.com
